{
  "texts": [
    "The RV-22 + DWT + SVM and DEV-22 + DWT + SVM models display robustness in the classification as a whole, with F1 scores of 92.8% and 93.5%, respectively.",
    "The inclusion of SVM as the final classifier significantly enhanced the system's efficacy.",
    "This demonstrates that SVM is a highly effective tool for the detection of colorectal cancer, as the results are consistent and dependable in all of the critical metrics.",
    "Figure 11 illustrates the bar chart.",
    "The RV-22 + DWT + SVM and DEV-22 + DWT + SVM models demonstrate accuracy and AUC scores throughout their training, validation, and testing phases."
  ]
}